the pictures.

01:29:07.654 --> 01:29:09.824
Photos,
whole bunch of them.

01:29:09.944 --> 01:29:12.574
They traced it back
to a mouse.

01:29:13.101 --> 01:29:15.018
That's what it looks like
anyway.

01:29:23.783 --> 01:29:25.100
Porter.

01:29:28.292 --> 01:29:30.918
